.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Nm stdc_bit_width_ Ns Em type Ns ()
family of functions and the
.Fn stdc_bit_width
type-generic macro conform to
.St -isoC-2023 .
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm stdc_bit_width_ Ns Em type Ns ()
family of functions and the
.Fn stdc_bit_width
type-generic macro were added in
.Fx 15.1.
